'''吉姆·布雷耶'''（{{lang-en|James W. Breyer}}, {{bd|1961年|7月26日||}})<ref name="Wealth-X">{{cite web |url=http://www.wealthx.com/articles/2015/james-w-breyer/ |title=Billionaires: James W. Breyer |publisher=Wealth-X |accessdate=2017-01-03 |archive-date=2017-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170103170223/http://www.wealthx.com/articles/2015/james-w-breyer/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 是一位匈牙利裔美国风险投资家，布雷耶资本创始人。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2017/09/22/billionaire-investor-jim-breyer-on-why-big-technology-growth-stocks-will-keep-surging.html|title=Billionaire investor Jim Breyer on why big technology growth stocks will keep surging|last=Franck|first=Thomas|date=2017-09-22|work=CNBC|access-date=2017-10-27|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206055512/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/09/22/billionaire-investor-jim-breyer-on-why-big-technology-growth-stocks-will-keep-surging.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://money.cnn.com/galleries/2010/technology/1007/gallery.smartest_people_tech.fortune/36.html |title=Smartest investor: Jim Breyer |work=[[CNNMoney|CNNMoney]] |date=July 9, 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100724155740/http://money.cnn.com/galleries/2010/technology/1007/gallery.smartest_people_tech.fortune/36.html |archivedate=2010-07-24 |accessdate=2020-12-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>投资过[[Facebook|Facebook]]，<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-18/accel-s-facebook-bet-poised-to-become-biggest-ever-venture-profit-tech.html |title=Accel Facebook Bet Poised to Become Biggest Venture Profit: Tech |author=Ari Levy |work=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg]] |date=January 18, 2012 |accessdate=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2016-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223180702/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-18/accel-s-facebook-bet-poised-to-become-biggest-ever-venture-profit-tech.html/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>盈利超过100倍，其他投资大多超过25倍。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2012/05/22/idUS144793+22-May-2012+BW20120522 |title=Brightcove PLAY 2012 to Feature Special Keynote Conversation with Jim Breyer, Erick Schonfeld & Jeremy Allaire |work=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |date=May 22, 2012 |accessdate=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924164107/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/05/22/idUS144793%2B22-May-2012%2BBW20120522 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==生平==
1961年出生于[[美国|美国]][[纽黑文|纽黑文]]的一个匈牙利犹太家庭，<ref name=HBSDoneDeal>[http://hbswk.hbs.edu/archive/1798.html Harvard Business School: "Done Deals: Venture Capitalists Tell Their Story: Featured HBS Alum Breyer" Excerpted from the book Done Deals, edited by Udayan Gupta] {{Wayback|url=http://hbswk.hbs.edu/archive/1798.html |date=20170927120634 }} December 4, 2000</ref><ref name="HBSAB">{{cite journal |url=https://www.alumni.hbs.edu/stories/Pages/story-bulletin.aspx?num=634 |title=One-on-One with Jim Breyer |author=Thompson, Roger |journal=Harvard School of Business Alumni Bulletin |date=March 2008 |access-date=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2020-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012194304/https://www.alumni.hbs.edu/stories/Pages/story-bulletin.aspx?num=634 |dead-url=no }}</ref>父亲是工程师，任职于[[国际数据集团|国际数据集团]]，<ref name="HBSAB" /><ref>[http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=816887&privcapId=22297 Businessweek: "John P. Breyer – Chairman, IDG Capital Partners] retrieved October 24, 2013</ref>母亲任职于[[霍尼韦尔|霍尼韦尔]]。<ref name=HBSDoneDeal />1983年毕业于[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]。<ref name=HBSDoneDeal /><ref name="BreyerElect">{{Cite news |url=http://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2013/02/breyer_elected/ |title=Breyer elected to Harvard Corporation |date=February 4, 2013 |publisher=[[Harvard_Gazette|Harvard Gazette]] |accessdate=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117172523/https://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2013/02/breyer_elected/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BreyerElect" /><ref>{{Cite web|date=2013-02-04|title=Breyer elected to Harvard Corporation|url=https://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2013/02/breyer_elected/|access-date=2020-10-19|website=Harvard Gazette|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424171900/https://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2013/02/breyer_elected/|dead-url=no}}</ref>毕业后任职于[[纽约|纽约]][[麦肯锡|麦肯锡]]。<ref name="forbes1">{{Cite news |url=https://www.forbes.com/2011/04/06/midas-list-11-jim-breyer-venture-capital-comeback-kid.html |title=The Comeback Kid |author=Nicole Perlroth |work=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |date=April 6, 2011 |accessdate=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025233212/https://www.forbes.com/2011/04/06/midas-list-11-jim-breyer-venture-capital-comeback-kid.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>1987年毕业于[[哈佛商学院|哈佛商学院]]。<ref>[http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/blog/2013/02/accels-jim-breyer-joins-harvard-corp.html San Francisco business Times: "Accel's Jim Breyer joins Harvard Corp" by Patrick Hoge] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/blog/2013/02/accels-jim-breyer-joins-harvard-corp.html |date=20160630014127 }} February 4, 2013</ref>1987年进入[[旧金山|旧金山]]的一家投资公司，<ref name=HBSDoneDeal />1990年成为其合伙人，1995年升迁为管理层合伙人。<ref name="BreyerElect" />其公司拥有仅次于[[马克·扎克伯格|马克·扎克伯格]]的11%的[[Facebook|Facebook]]股票。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://money.cnn.com/2012/02/01/technology/facebook_ipo_zuckerberg/ |title=Zuckerberg's Facebook stake is worth at least $16 billion |author=David Goldman |publisher=[[CNNMoney|CNNMoney]] |date=February 2, 2012 |accessdate=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2018-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205185032/http://money.cnn.com/2012/02/01/technology/facebook_ipo_zuckerberg/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2006年成立布雷耶资本，<ref name="forbes1" />主要投资于[[中国|中国]]，[[巴西|巴西]]和[[印度|印度]]。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/47387334 |title=Jim Breyer (via Accel Partners) |publisher=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |date=May 22, 2012 |accessdate=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2020-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802171203/https://www.cnbc.com/id/47387334 |dead-url=no }}</ref>曾担任[[Facebook|Facebook]]和[[沃尔玛|沃尔玛]]董事会成员。

